Rogue archaeologist Doctor Aphra is not stranger to risk in the pursuit of both credits and thrills. Now, having successfully faked her own death at Darth Vader's hands, Aphra is back to doing what she does best: locating and liberating rare artifacts, droid and Wookiee companions by her side....
The voice talent is provided by members of Casting Call Club (https://castingcall.club).
